title: Wtf? Im confused
body:
https://matchhistory.na.leagueoflegends.com/en/#match-details/NA1/2941719683/219935142?tab=stats

Check out Damaged Healed.  

For a Champion who sacrificed ALOT for built in Sustain im confused
  How a Teemo with no in built Sustain out Healed me by several Thousands.  What Runes is he running?

I must be missing Something.

replies.body:
Redbuff, blessing of soraka, smite.
Without a replay it's hard to know where this heal come from.

But i've noticed some weird values when i was working with riot's API. Like hundreds (even thousands) of true damages on a champion who didn't have any rune, skill or item to do so. Haven't found why it's like this :/

> [{quoted}](name=Hi Im a Cat,realm=NA,application-id=3ErqAdtq,discussion-id=AetPqEfm,comment-id=0000,timestamp=2018-12-29T02:20:45.297+0000)
>
> Smiting camps heals you.

Thats part of it im sure but does that account for such a Large amount of healing. That cant be the only factor
Was he running domination?  Ravenous hunter probably works well with his high damage output.

Jungle items and smite contribute a lot.

Still WTF though.
